      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, this example is a mechanical masterpiece featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. The 3.2L straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the entire power band. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal power delivery. Suspension kinematics are factory-sharp, benefiting from a complete bushing refresh and precise alignment. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen for the driver who demands peak atmospheric performance and structural integrity.",
