      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2018 BMW M3 Competition in Yas Marina Blue. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the Silverstone Extended Merino leather remains supple and firm, still carrying that new-car aroma, with no visible wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a thick folder of documentation to prove it. The 20-inch forged wheels are free of curb rash and wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Mechanically, it is perfect\u2014no leaks, no noises, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
